155
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:46,980
And now,

156
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:48,940
I'm leaving you.

157
00:07:58,780 --> 00:07:59,620
Brother,

158
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,540
