224
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:10,940
Also,

225
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:12,340
hadn't I fired that signal shell,

226
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,740
Division 234 would have been cleared at Zhangmu,

227
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:15,580
