286
00:14:15,220 --> 00:14:16,540
It’s so boring that I quitted.

287
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:17,940
I felt like I should

288
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:20,220
serve my country like my brother,

289
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:22,300
